---
title: Jerk-Style Double Jumbo Shrimp Tacos with Crunchy Red Cabbage Slaw and Pineapple-Tomato Salsa
description: Spice up your life with a taste of the islands and these juicy jerk-seasoned shrimp tacos. A zippy and refreshing red cabbage coleslaw brings some crunch, while a salsa of shallots, tomatoes, cilantro and pineapple provides freshness and sweetness!
